snippet.title: NARUTO X BORUTO Ultimate Ninja STORM CONNECTIONS – DLC Pack 3: Kurenai Yuhi Trailer
snippet.description:
At last! Yuhi Kurenai joins the fray in DLC Pack 3, out May 30 for NARUTO X BORUTO Ultimate Ninja STORM CONNECTIONS!

【DLC Pack 3 Additional Content】
・Secret Combination:
“Evil Illusion: Tree Bind Wind Blade” – Kurenai x Asuma
“Six Paths: Shinsu Rasen Shuriken” – Ashura x Hashirama x Naruto
・Matching Voice x 12
・Ninja Info Card Image x 5
#NSC
